Model Creations¶

In [22]:
def Train(model,x_train,y_train,x_test,y_test):
    model.fit(x_train,y_train)
    print(f'Model:{model}')
    print()
    print('Model Report:')
    print()
    print('Prediction on Training Data:') 
    train_preds = model.predict(x_train)
    print(train_preds)
    print()
    print('Accuracy on Training Data:')
    print(accuracy_score(y_train, train_preds))
    print()
    print('Prediction on Testing Data:')
    test_preds = model.predict(x_test)
    print(test_preds)
    print()
    print('Accuracy on Testing Data:')
    print(accuracy_score(y_test, test_preds))
    print()
    print('Kappa Score :',cohen_kappa_score(y_test,test_preds))
    print()
    print('*'*100)
    print()
    print("Confusion Matrix for Training Data:\n ", confusion_matrix(y_train, train_preds))
    print()
    print("Confusion Matrix for Testing Data:\n ", confusion_matrix(y_test, test_preds))
    print()
    print('\nClassification Report of Training Data: ')
    print(classification_report (y_train, train_preds))
    print()
    print('\nClassification Report of Testing Data: ')
    print(classification_report (y_test, test_preds))
